text:
⛺Along the Boardwalk at the eastern end of the Pond are two View Decks found in front of Blk 405 and Blk 406.
⛺⛺The two sheltered View Decks allow visitors to enjoy a panoramic view of the picturesque pond and it's lush surrounding comfortably shielded from the natural elements.
⛺The two View Decks are fitted with benches that visitors can relax on.
